subproject.description: The project is for the implementation of the Global Fund Round 5 TB Grant .  The objectives of the grant are: (i) To strengthen laboratory Services for diagnosis; (ii) To improve treatment outcomes by improving case management and support of tuberculosis patients and (iii) To develop and implement TB & HIV collaborative activities at all implementation levels
